sp.p:
I have served Prince Florizel and in my time
wore three-pile;
but now I am out of service:

Come on, lay it by: and let's first see
moe ballads;
we'll buy the other things anon.

I can bear my part; you must know
'tis my occupation;
have at it with you. SONG.
